keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.
unmap r
unmap t
unmap h
unmap x
unmap X
unmap p
unmap P
map gp togglePinTab
map gm toggleMuteTab
map gc closeOtherTabs
map gx0 closeTabsOnLeft
map gx$ closeTabsOnRight
